{"tid":1212059,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[台灣殺人案] [公義？] 一旦通過逃犯條例，殺人犯將一世逍遙法外","createTime":"2019-06-12T17:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T18:36:21.000Z","uid":56982,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f3119afa342425b7da59aa0317aca8b09dd31995","tid":1212059,"uid":56982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:12:56.000Z","msg":"林鄭琴日又拿台灣殺人案出黎講，動之以情對中間派好殺食，尤其是師奶。<br />\n<br />\n完全唔明點解無記著/議員追問，明明台灣都助曬攻，連總統蔡英文都講到明唔會係逃犯條例下引渡陳同佳[1]。咁樣前題下，姐係。。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一旦通過逃犯條例，殺人犯將一世逍遙法外</span></span><br />\n<br />\n台灣肯定就唔引渡，之前李家超亦話唔會引渡佢返大陸[3]，而香港亦告唔到佢謀殺，咁姐係佢坐完單洗黑錢就會大搖大擺係香港周圍走，亦姐係隨時有個殺人犯係你左近，亦都無法為潘生潘太的女兒伸冤，所有佢之前講的論點全部反彈返畀自己<br />\n<br />\n和理非非同抗爭外，亦都要係輿論拿返個道德高地，拉埋中間派，尤其是師奶支持，佢地唔會理咩一國兩制咩司法制度，更多會代入死者家屬的感受－殺人要得到審判，所以與其花時間解釋個制度點樣有漏洞去引渡香港人(佢地覺得杞人憂天跟住你又要解釋一大輪或者去辯論)，不如廣傳一個鐵一般的事實<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一旦通過逃犯條例，殺人犯將一世逍遙法外</span></span><br />\n<br />\n真係要彰顯公義，應該一次性引渡或只引渡去司法制度完善的國家，立法會可以無爭議咁係陳同佳出獄前通過，台灣亦願意引渡佢返去受審<br />\n<br />\n唔好再畀政府用陳同佳做借口！<br />\n<br />\n<ins>參考資料</ins><br />\n[1] 蔡英文：中華民國政府也已經一再重申，絕不會接受任何以消滅國家主權為目的之作為，也拒絕接受以修法為前提的個案移交<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mac.gov.tw/cp.aspx?n=B3FBDF70D23B706E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mac.gov.tw%2Fcp.aspx%3Fn%3DB3FBDF70D23B706E&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMZrbLZzzsfwfKyNyJagnZM4%3D&h=991aeb09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mac.gov.tw/cp.aspx?n=B3FBDF70D23B706E</a><br />\n<br />\n[2] 台灣陸委會重申立場，拒絕接受以修法為前提的個案移交<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/338611/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E9%99%B8%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-%E7%94%B1%E8%A1%B7%E6%84%9F%E4%BD%A9%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E9%87%8D%E7%94%B3%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E7%A7%BB%E4%BA%A4%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F338611%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E-%25E7%2594%25B1%25E8%25A1%25B7%25E6%2584%259F%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2594%25B3%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%25B5%2595%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%25A0%25B4&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMZrbLZzzsfwfKyNyJagnZM4%3D&h=06de3329\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/338611/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E9%99%B8%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-%E7%94%B1%E8%A1%B7%E6%84%9F%E4%BD%A9%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E9%87%8D%E7%94%B3%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E7%A7%BB%E4%BA%A4%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4</a><br />\n<br />\n[3] 李家超：嚴正聲明不移送陳同佳返大陸<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/335696/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85-%E5%9A%B4%E6%AD%A3%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%E4%B8%8D%E7%A7%BB%E9%80%81%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E8%BF%94%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8-%E6%8B%92%E8%A9%95%E5%8A%89%E9%91%BE%E9%9B%84%E6%A1%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F335696%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585-%25E5%259A%25B4%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E8%25BF%2594%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8-%25E6%258B%2592%25E8%25A9%2595%25E5%258A%2589%25E9%2591%25BE%25E9%259B%2584%25E6%25A1%2588&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMZrbLZzzsfwfKyNyJagnZM4%3D&h=22dd6855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/335696/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85-%E5%9A%B4%E6%AD%A3%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%E4%B8%8D%E7%A7%BB%E9%80%81%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E8%BF%94%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8-%E6%8B%92%E8%A9%95%E5%8A%89%E9%91%BE%E9%9B%84%E6%A1%88</a>"},{"pid":"9dbc3df2bb38574a0dd5551cbf5fe7ea94a45163","tid":1212059,"uid":5499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:20:59.000Z","msg":"姐係承認台獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76de9e8617470ff2f2491c61a07b3b23f6251f5b","tid":1212059,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:24:46.000Z","msg":"問題係、輿論一早比港共控制哂"},{"pid":"b8ff37b44bdac52b661d0c0906569db5e3f49448","tid":1212059,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:36:41.000Z","msg":"一定有其他方法入陳同佳<br />\n但政府唔做 多多藉口"},{"pid":"e32e05b55f45d50a68d2a28d6898880ac42e5e39","tid":1212059,"uid":56982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76de9e8617470ff2f2491c61a07b3b23f6251f5b","tid":1212059,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:24:46.000Z","msg":"問題係、輿論一早比港共控制哂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:56:12.000Z","msg":"林鄭開記者會／泛民自己記者會講出黎／你知道嗎長輩圖攻勢？"},{"pid":"205d85cc6821f1ca662a2f2c79a54f0aeb9975cb","tid":1212059,"uid":56982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:05:18.000Z","msg":"劣作<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WUMCZQ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWUMCZQ1.jpg&h=60c38840&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa4784249dbbb27ac4988c4edf31fd385a436d10","tid":1212059,"uid":56982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}